less visual noise.

6
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.940
Don't keep your phone close -
put it away.

7
00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:21.690
You don't need it.

8
00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:25.860
Moving yourself to another location and only 
concentrating on the task at hand

9
00:00:26.280 --> 00:00:28.130,
it simply increases your focus.

10
